00:37:46,167 --> 00:37:48,059
DON'T "SIR" ME.

863
00:37:48,083 --> 00:37:50,560
DON'T FEED ME THAT
"SIR" BUSINESS.

864
00:37:50,584 --> 00:37:52,560
YOU PUNCHED THIS
GUY IN THE MOUTH.

865
00:37:52,584 --> 00:37:54,185
ON WHAT BASIS?

866
00:37:54,209 --> 00:37:56,975
SIR, SIR, HE STARTED MOUTHING
OFF, STARTED LAUGHING, SO...

867
00:37:56,999 --> 00:38:00,643
Dean: YEAH, THAT DOESN'T
GIVE YOU A RIGHT TO HIT HIM.

868
00:38:00,667 --> 00:38:04,310
IF IT WAS A 6' 2",
215-POUND FULLBACK,

869
00:38:04,334 --> 00:38:08,101
YOU WOULDN'T BE SO QUICK
TO PUNCH HIM IN THE MOUTH.

870
00:38:08,125 --> 00:38:10,768
P-E-R-G.

871
00:38:10,792 --> 00:38:12,518
Boy: O-L-I-N-O.

872
00:38:12,542 --> 00:38:14,667
WHERE DO YOU COME
IN TO HIT THIS GUY?

873
00:38:18,292 --> 00:38:20,268
HE HAS A RIGHT TO
ERASE THE BOARD.

874
00:38:20,292 --> 00:38:22,435
Boy: THAT'S NOT
WHAT IT WAS OVER.

875
00:38:22,459 --> 00:38:25,310
Dean: JUST AS MUCH AS YOU
HAVE A RIGHT TO WRITE ON IT.

876
00:38:25,334 --> 00:38:26,975
YOU DIDN'T ASK PERMISSION

877
00:38:26,999 --> 00:38:28,560
TO WRITE THOSE NAMES
ON THE BOARD, DID YOU?

878
00:38:28,584 --> 00:38:30,602
PARDON ME, SIR, BUT THAT
WASN'T WHAT IT WAS OVER.

879
00:38:30,626 --> 00:38:32,518
WHAT WAS IT OVER?

880
00:38:32,542 --> 00:38:34,518
SIR, JUST BEFORE CLASS STARTED,

881
00:38:34,542 --> 00:38:36,852
WE HAD AN ARGUMENT, AND
I DIDN'T DO NOTHING.

882
00:38:36,876 --> 00:38:39,768
WELL, YOU'RE NOT
SUPPOSEDTO DO ANYTHING.

883
00:38:39,792 --> 00:38:41,975
YOU DON'T STRIKE OR HIT ANYBODY.

884
00:38:41,999 --> 00:38:43,894
LEVINE WEARS GLASSES
ON TOP OF IT,

885
00:38:43,918 --> 00:38:45,560
YET YOU STILL HIT HIM.

886
00:38:45,584 --> 00:38:47,226
SIR, I WEAR GLASSES, TOO.

887
00:38:47,250 --> 00:38:49,226
