HOLD ON, HOLD ON.

1557
01:07:38,918 --> 01:07:40,435
SCOTT, GOOD JOB.

1558
01:07:40,459 --> 01:07:41,935
THANK YOU.

1559
01:07:41,959 --> 01:07:44,975
DICK CASEY'S HERE.

1560
01:07:44,999 --> 01:07:47,768
HEY, SCOTT, MAN.
SCOTT, HOW YOU DOING?

1561
01:07:47,792 --> 01:07:50,477
SCOTT.

1562
01:07:50,501 --> 01:07:53,101
SCOTT.

1563
01:07:53,125 --> 01:07:55,143
WE RECEIVED A TELEGRAM
THIS MORNING.

1564
01:07:55,167 --> 01:07:57,185
I WANT TO READ IT AT THIS TIME.

1565
01:07:57,209 --> 01:08:00,018
"STUDENTS AND FACULTY OF
NORTHEAST HIGH SCHOOL,

1566
01:08:00,042 --> 01:08:01,643
"ATTENTION: ROBERT MONTGOMERY.

1567
01:08:01,667 --> 01:08:03,310
"I SHOULD LIKE TO TAKE
THIS OPPORTUNITY TO EXTEND

1568
01:08:03,334 --> 01:08:05,059
"MY BEST WISHES TO EACH OF YOU

1569
01:08:05,083 --> 01:08:07,393
"FOR YOUR CONTINUED SUCCESS
WITH PROJECT SPARC.

1570
01:08:07,417 --> 01:08:10,143
"SPECIFICALLY MY HEARTIEST
CONGRATULATIONS

1571
01:08:10,167 --> 01:08:14,226
"TO ASTRONAUTS JAN GABIN,
HARVEY RUBIN, AND SCOTT CHERRY,

1572
01:08:14,250 --> 01:08:18,018
UPON COMPLETION OF 193 HOURS
OF SIMULATED FLIGHT."

1573
01:08:18,042 --> 01:08:20,477
THE TELEGRAM COMES FROM L.
GORDON COOPER,

1574
01:08:20,501 --> 01:08:21,975
NASA ASTRONAUT.

1575
01:08:21,999 --> 01:08:23,685
[ APPLAUSE ]

1576
01:08:23,709 --> 01:08:25,643
I'M GOING TO CRY.

1577
01:08:25,667 --> 01:08:28,768
I'M ALL MISTY, MAN.

1578
01:08:28,792 --> 01:08:31,975
GETTING ALL MISTY.

1579
01:08:32,000 --> 01:08:34,184
THIS IS MAN NUMBER ONE,

1580
01:08:34,209 --> 01:08:38,268
NUMBER TWO, NUMBER THREE, OKAY?

1581
01:08:38,292 --> 01:08:40,082
GET A LITTLE CLOSER.

1582
01:08:43,542 --> 01:08:45,792
Woman: HEY, HOW ARE YOU?

1583
01:08:47,999 --> 01:08:49,393
Man: GOOD MORNING, HOW ARE YOU?

1584
01:08:49,417 --> 01:08:52,268
Boy: RUBIN, HEY.

1585
01:08:52,292 --> 01:08:54,999
SCOTT.

1586
01:09:05,209 --> 01:09:06,975
DRUMS.

1587
01:09:06,999 --> 01:09:07,975
ROLL.

1588
01:09:07,999 --> 01:09:09,167
[ DRUMS BEAT ]

1589
01:09:13,334 --> 01:09:15,167
[ PLAYING "HEY, LOOK ME OVER" ]

1590
01:10:18,834 --> 01:10:21,559
NOW, LET ME READ YOU THIS ONE...

1591
01:10:21,584 --> 01:10:25,975
IF I'M ABLE TO GET THROUGH IT.

1592
01:10:25,999 --> 01:10:30,268
THIS IS WRITTEN FROM...
AND I MIGHT SAY THAT

1593
01:10:30,292 --> 01:10:34,602
THE LETTER I'M ABOUT TO
READ IS FROM BOB WALTERS.

1594
01:10:34,626 --> 01:10:37,975
BOB WALTERS, AS FRAN
COULD TELL YOU...

1595
01:10:37,999 --> 01:10:41,975
SHE COULD WRITE HIS BIOGRAPHY...

1596
01:10:41,999 --> 01:10:48,559
WAS A BOY WITHOUT PARENTS WHO
MIGHT HAVE BEEN A NOBODY.

1597
01:10:48,584 --> 01:10:51,018
HE CERTAINLY WAS NOT A
HIGH ACADEMIC STUDENT.

1598
01:10:51,042 --> 01:10:55,268
HE WAS MOST AVERAGE OR
SUB-AVERAGE IN MANY WAYS.

1599
01:10:55,292 --> 01:10:57,709
BUT A FEW TEACHERS WHO CARED...

1600
01:10:59,792 --> 01:11:03,393
MADE A GREAT DIFFERENCE
IN THIS BOY'S LIFE.

1601
01:11:03,417 --> 01:11:10,809
HIS LETTER COMES ON STATIONERY
MARKED "USSOKINAWA."

1602
01:11:10,834 --> 01:11:12,768
I HOPE I CAN GET THROUGH IT.

1603
01:11:12,792 --> 01:11:15,975
IF I DON'T, HY,
YOU'LL HAVE TO GO ON.

1604
01:11:15,999 --> 01:11:18,434
DEAR DR. HALLER,

1605
01:11:18,459 --> 01:11:22,309
I HAVE ONLY A FEW
HOURS BEFORE I GO.

1606
01:11:22,334 --> 01:11:25,975
TODAY I WILL TAKE A PLANE
TRIP FROM THIS SHIP.

1607
01:11:25,999 --> 01:11:29,101
I PRAY THAT I'LL MAKE IT BACK,

1608
01:11:29,125 --> 01:11:32,184
BUT IT IS ALL IN
GOD'S HANDS NOW.

1609
01:11:32,209 --> 01:11:35,975
YOU SEE, I AM GOING
WITH THREE OTHER MEN.

1610
01:11:35,999 --> 01:11:37,602
WE ARE GOING TO BE DROPPED

1611
01:11:37,626 --> 01:11:43,393
BEHIND THE DMZ... THE
DEMILITARIZED ZONE.

1612
01:11:43,417 --> 01:11:45,393
THE REASON FOR
TELLING YOU THIS IS

1613
01:11:45,417 --> 01:11:47,518
THAT ALL MY INSURANCE MONEY

1614
01:11:47,542 --> 01:11:49,768
WILL BE GIVEN FOR
THAT SCHOLARSHIP

1615
01:11:49,792 --> 01:11:52,975
I ONCE STARTED BUT
NEVER FINISHED

1616
01:11:52,999 --> 01:11:54,602
IF I DON'T MAKE IT BACK.

1617
01:11:54,626 --> 01:11:58,809
I AM ONLY INSURED FOR $10,000.

1618
01:11:58,834 --> 01:12:01,975
MAYBE IT COULD HELP SOMEONE.

1619
01:12:01,999 --> 01:12:06,143
I HAVE BEEN TRYING TO BECOME
A BIG BROTHER IN VIETNAM,

1620
01:12:06,167 --> 01:12:09,226
BUT IT IS VERY HARD TO DO.

1621
01:12:09,250 --> 01:12:12,226
I HAVE TO WRITE BACK AND FORTH
TO SAN DIEGO, CALIFORNIA,

1622
01:12:12,250 --> 01:12:13,975
AND THAT TAKES TIME.

1623
01:12:13,999 --> 01:12:17,477
I ONLY HOPE THAT I AM GOOD
ENOUGH TO BECOME ONE.

1624
01:12:17,501 --> 01:12:19,226
GOD ONLY KNOWS.

1625
01:12:19,250 --> 01:12:23,059
I REALLY PRAY THAT THE YOUNG
MEN IN YOUR COOKING CLASSES

1626
01:12:23,083 --> 01:12:26,852
WILL USE THIS CHANGE
OF LEARNING VERY WELL.

1627
01:12:26,876 --> 01:12:28,309
THANK YOU, DR. HALLER,

1628
01:12:28,334 --> 01:12:31,975
FOR HELPING THESE MEN BECOME
GOOD, VERY FINE COOKS.

1629
01:12:31,999 --> 01:12:34,684
HE SHOULD HAVE SAID,
"THANK YOU, MRS. C."

1630
01:12:34,709 --> 01:12:38,894
MY PERSONAL FAMILY USUALLY
DOESN'T UNDERSTAND ME.

1631
01:12:38,918 --> 01:12:45,518
THEY DON'T UNDERSTAND WHY I
HAVE TO DO WHAT I DO DO.

1632
01:12:45,542 --> 01:12:48,975
THEY SAY THAT I'M A REAL
NUT TO DO SUCH WORK,

1633
01:12:48,999 --> 01:12:52,184
BUT...

1634
01:12:52,209 --> 01:12:54,434
THUS THEY SAY,

1635
01:12:54,459 --> 01:12:57,852
"DON'T YOU VALUE LIFE?
ARE YOU CRAZY?"

1636
01:12:57,876 --> 01:12:59,226
MY ANSWER IS... "YES.

1637
01:12:59,250 --> 01:13:02,602
"BUT I VALUE ALL THE
LIVES OF SOUTH VIETNAM

1638
01:13:02,626 --> 01:13:04,559
"AND THE FREE WORLD

1639
01:13:04,584 --> 01:13:08,975
SO THAT THEY AND ALL OF
US CAN LIVE IN PEACE."

1640
01:13:08,999 --> 01:13:10,727
AM I WRONG, DR. HALLER?

1641
01:13:10,751 --> 01:13:14,975
IF I DO MY BEST ALL THE TIME
AND BELIEVE IN WHAT I DO,

1642
01:13:14,999 --> 01:13:16,934
BELIEVE THAT WHAT I DO IS RIGHT,

1643
01:13:16,959 --> 01:13:18,975
THAT IS ALL I CAN DO.

1644
01:13:18,999 --> 01:13:21,894
DR. HALLER, IF ANYTHING
HAPPENS TO ME,

1645
01:13:21,918 --> 01:13:23,602
JAMES C. HECKWICKER...

1646
01:13:23,626 --> 01:13:24,976
I THINK IT IS...

1647
01:13:25,000 --> 01:13:26,809
WILL SEND YOU A TELEGRAM,

1648
01:13:26,834 --> 01:13:29,643
AND IN TIME, HE WILL
SEND YOU THE MONEY.

1649
01:13:29,667 --> 01:13:32,226
PLEASE DON'T SAY ANYTHING TO MRS.
C....

1650
01:13:32,250 --> 01:13:33,975
BUT I DID.

1651
01:13:33,999 --> 01:13:35,975
SHE WOULD ONLY WORRY OVER ME.

1652
01:13:35,999 --> 01:13:37,643
I AM NOT WORTH IT.

1653
01:13:37,667 --> 01:13:41,894
I AM ONLY A BODY DOING A JOB.

1654
01:13:41,918 --> 01:13:44,101
IN CLOSING, I THANK EVERYONE

1655
01:13:44,125 --> 01:13:47,351
FOR WHAT THEY ALL
HAVE DONE FOR ME.

1656
01:13:47,375 --> 01:13:49,809
YOURS TRULY, BOB WALTERS.

1657
01:13:49,834 --> 01:13:51,975
THANK YOU ALL AGAIN VERY MUCH.

1658
01:13:51,999 --> 01:13:53,975
PLEASE FORGIVE MY HANDWRITING.

1659
01:13:53,999 --> 01:13:55,727
I AM A LITTLE JUMPY.

1660
01:13:55,751 --> 01:13:58,268
PLEASE UNDERSTAND.

1661
01:13:58,292 --> 01:14:01,143
NOW, WHEN YOU GET A
LETTER LIKE THIS,

1662
01:14:01,167 --> 01:14:04,143
TO ME, IT MEANS

1663
01:14:04,167 --> 01:14:09,101
THAT WE ARE VERY SUCCESSFUL
AT NORTHEAST HIGH SCHOOL.

1664
01:14:09,125 --> 01:14:11,192
I THINK YOU WILL AGREE WITH ME.
